## 🪄 Cursor Behavior Rules

- **Do not modify** `docs/about/About-me.mdx` (it’s finalized).  
- **When adding new course folders** under `/docs/hsu/`, use consistent naming:  
  `COURSECODE-Course-Title`  
  e.g., `SW206DL01-Algorithms-Analysis-and-Design`
- **Each course folder must contain:**
  - `index.mdx` – Overview  
  - `weekX-topic.mdx` – Lesson files  
  - `diagrams/` – Optional `.mmd` / `.plantuml` diagrams
- **Auto-generate frontmatter** for each new `.mdx`:
  ```mdx
  ---
  title: Week 1 - Introduction
  sidebar_label: Week 1 - Introduction
  description: Notes and diagrams for SW206DL01
  ---
  ```
- **Automatically register** new docs in `sidebars.ts`
- **Group** all Docusaurus sample docs under `docs/samples/`
- **Render** math and diagrams correctly in Markdown using:
  - `remark-mermaidjs` for flowcharts / UML
  - `remark-math` + `rehype-katex` for LaTeX math
- **Enable** live code blocks via `@docusaurus/theme-live-codeblock`
- **Ensure** sitemap and analytics plugins are active

